title: Weekly Review Podcast - Sample - Week 1
description: This is a sample version of a weekly review podcast which is normally part of the Premium feed. The review podcast will help you go over everything you've covered in the course of the week. It links to the pdf vocabulary guide which is also available and more explanations of the words and phrases covered each day are provided, allowing you to get more out your learning experience.
